  <h3 style="text-align:center">Objective</h3>

  <p style="margin-left:20%;margin-right:20%">The project was taken up with the aim to redesign and reintroduce the James Bond game franchise back into the modern world. The James Bond Video games from the 90s were the most successful and sought after videogames of the period.</p><br />

  <h3 style="text-align:center">My Role</h3>

  <p style="margin-left:20%;margin-right:20%">My work aimed at reintroducing the franchise, produced the conception and design of 007 elixir, a sandbox game with extremely realistic graphics and mechanics based on the Rockstar Advanced Game Engine (RAGE).</p><br />

  <h3 style="text-align:center">Outcome</h3>

  <p style="margin-left:20%;margin-right:20%">A new parallel mission line plot mechanic was created to increase replay value and leave room for future sequels.With this game, a new reactive narrative has been created known as the ‘Hybrid Narrative’, which continually responds and reacts to the player’s successes and failures across the course of the game, leading to greatly enhanced replay value of the game.We have also introduced a new memoirs mode. The memoirs mode is based on an old and retired Bond reminiscing over the various missions he participated in, in his younger days. This gives us endless room for future sequels. It also blends in perfectly with our HYBRID narrative, where actions of the player alter the story greatly.
  </p><br />

